408
00:23:35,180 --> 00:23:35,980
No need.

409
00:23:57,100 --> 00:23:57,660
Mr. Fang.

410
00:23:57,780 --> 00:23:58,300
You...

411
00:23:58,820 --> 00:23:59,500
Have some tea.

412
00:23:59,940 --> 00:24:01,050
