464
00:26:37,380 --> 00:26:37,660
You…

465
00:26:38,500 --> 00:26:40,340
Is this how you top students win girls' hearts?

466
00:26:41,980 --> 00:26:42,670
Well,

467
00:26:42,810 --> 00:26:45,500
