504
00:28:03,250 --> 00:28:04,780
Those articles make it clear that…

505
00:28:15,220 --> 00:28:15,820
Mr. Fang.

506
00:28:15,820 --> 00:28:16,620
I'd love to

507
00:28:16,700 --> 00:28:18,740
