534
00:29:35,820 --> 00:29:37,300
How?

535
00:29:37,340 --> 00:29:39,140
Your pockets are empty.

536
00:29:39,140 --> 00:29:41,140
The shooting will start soon.

537
00:29:41,140 --> 00:29:43,050
