549
00:30:27,300 --> 00:30:28,180
No emotion at all.

550
00:30:28,180 --> 00:30:29,980
It's so flat.

551
00:30:29,980 --> 00:30:31,420
No dynamics.

552
00:30:31,770 --> 00:30:32,780
Mr. Fang.

553
00:30:33,180 --> 00:30:35,500
